//#############################
      // WEST
      //#############################

      for(i=0;i<WE_DOMAINS;i=i+1)
	begin: we_pads
	   oh_pads_domain #(.DIR("WE"),
			    .TYPE(TYPE),
			    .NGPIO(WE_GPIO),
			    .NVDDIO(WE_VDDIO),
			    .NVSSIO(WE_VSSIO),
			    .NVDD(WE_VDD),
			    .NVSS(WE_VSS),
			    .POC(1),
			    .LEFTCUT(1),
			    .RIGHTCUT(1))			    
	 
	   i0 (.vdd     (vdd),
	       .vss     (vss),
	       // Outputs
	       .din     (we_din[WE_GPIO-1:0]),
	       // Inouts
	       .pad     (we_pad[WE_GPIO-1:0]),
	       .vddio   (we_vddio[i]),
	       .vssio	(we_vssio[i]),
	       .poc	(we_poc[i]),
	       // Inputs
	       .dout	(we_dout[WE_GPIO-1:0]),
	       .oen	(we_oen[WE_GPIO-1:0]),
	       .ie	(we_ie[WE_GPIO-1:0]),
	       .cfg	(we_cfg[WE_GPIO*8-1:0]));
	   
	end
      
   endgenerate

endmodule // oh_padring
